{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everything begins again with a prophecy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But this time, will humanity once again receive the protection of fate?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The legendary Crown Priestess, Ashirselis, foresaw the corruption and collapse of fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But her prophecy was ridiculed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The nobles, blinded by decadence and luxury, ignored the warnings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ashirselis turned to her friend, Queen Leora, who sent the Crimson Knights with Ashirselis\u2019s message to investigate the borderlands...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On the border, facing relentless monsters, you will join the Crimson Knights to explore dungeons, uncover, and defeat the evil foretold by the Crown Priestess!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>Gameplay</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Turn-Based RPG:</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Assemble a team of knights and monsters, harnessing knights' combat power and monsters' unique traits to defeat incoming foes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Upgrade and allocate attribute points freely to learn more powerful skills!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Monsters drop various gear and resources to strengthen your team.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Roguelite:</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Each battle is a fresh start\u2014choose different attributes and skills to tackle the dungeon!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Randomly generated blessings provide varied development paths for your team.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Monsters in dungeons are randomly generated, enhancing 